General.Name: Aurora Royalties Inc
General.Description: Aurora Royalties Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and evaluation of resource properties Canada. The company was formerly known as Amato Exploration Ltd. and changed its name to Aurora Royalties Inc. in February 2018. Aurora Royalties Inc. was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
